msgid "Verify"
msgstr "Overiť"

#: ../../../app/views/users/two_factor/backup_codes.html.erb:1
#: ../../../app/views/users/two_factor/backup_codes.html.erb:6
msgid "Save your backup codes"
msgstr "Uloženie záložných kódov"

#: ../../../app/views/users/two_factor/backup_codes.html.erb:8
msgid ""
"Store these codes in a safe place. Each can be used once if you lose your auth"
"enticator device."
msgstr ""
"Tieto kódy uložte na bezpečné miesto. V prípade straty autentifikačného zariad"
"enia môžete každý z nich použiť len raz."

#: ../../../app/views/users/two_factor/backup_codes.html.erb:13
msgid "Save or copy these codes now"
msgstr "Uložte alebo skopírujte tieto kódy"

#: ../../../app/views/users/two_factor/backup_codes.html.erb:14
msgid ""
"You will not be able to see this list again after you continue. If you lose yo"
"ur device and your backup codes, you may need an administrator to reset your a"
"ccount."
msgstr ""
"Po pokračovaní už nebudete môcť tento zoznam zobraziť. Ak stratíte svoje zaria"
"denie a záložné kódy, môže byť potrebné, aby správca obnovil vaše konto."

#: ../../../app/views/users/two_factor/backup_codes.html.erb:20
msgid "Recovery codes"
msgstr "Kódy obnovy"

#: ../../../app/views/users/two_factor/backup_codes.html.erb:21
msgid "total"
msgstr "celkom"

#: ../../../app/views/users/two_factor/backup_codes.html.erb:37
#: ../../../app/views/users/two_factor/backup_codes.html.erb:38
msgid "Copy all codes"
msgstr "Skopírujte všetky kódy"

#: ../../../app/views/users/two_factor/backup_codes.html.erb:42
msgid ""
"Backup codes are saved but can only be shown once. If you did not save them, d"
"isable two-factor authentication and set it up again."
msgstr ""
"Záložné kódy sa uložia, ale môžu sa zobraziť len raz. Ak ste ich neuložili, vy"
"pnite dvojfaktorové overovanie a nastavte ho znova."

#: ../../../app/views/users/two_factor/backup_codes.html.erb:48
msgid "Continue to verify"
msgstr "Pokračujte v overovaní"

#: ../../../app/views/users/two_factor/verify.html.erb:1
msgid "Verify authenticator"
msgstr "Overenie autentifikátora"

#: ../../../app/views/users/two_factor/verify.html.erb:6
msgid "Scan this QR code"
msgstr "Naskenujte tento kód QR"

#: ../../../app/views/users/two_factor/verify.html.erb:7
msgid ""
"Add this account to your authenticator app, then enter the 6-digit code to con"
"firm."
msgstr ""
"Pridajte toto konto do aplikácie autentifikátora a potom zadajte 6-miestny kód"
" na potvrdenie."

#: ../../../app/views/users/two_factor/verify.html.erb:11
msgid "If you cannot scan the code, enter this secret manually:"
msgstr "Ak sa vám nepodarí naskenovať kód, zadajte toto tajomstvo ručne:"

#: ../../../app/views/users/two_factor/verify.html.erb:20
msgid "Enable two-factor authentication"
msgstr "Povolenie dvojfaktorového overovania"
